title: Ronan Keating's brother Ciaran killed in car crash
description: Singer Ronan Keating's brother Ciaran has been killed in a car crash in Co Mayo.

title: British backpacker 'stabbed in back at Australian beach resort'
description: A 25-year-old British backpacker has been stabbed in the back by a teenager in an Australian beach resort, local media is reporting.

title: Inside the Italian emergency response room where concerns over wildfires are rising
description: The situation room inside Italy's civil protection authority is humming with activity as the head of the emergency department, Carlo Constantini, circulates the space.

title: US tsunami warning issued after earthquake in Alaska Peninsula region

title: Netanyahu set to be released from hospital after dehydration
description: Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu is expected to be released from hospital on Sunday after suffering from dehydration.

title: 'A significant milestone for UK trade': Britain signs deal to join £12trn Indo-Pacific trading block
description: Kemi Badenoch has signed off UK membership to a major Indo-Pacific trade bloc.
